  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-primary-600 bg-primary-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Guides</span>
      <span class="text-xs text-neutral-400 ml-3">Updated March 2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">Gas Bill Consumer Number — SNGPL & SSGC Guide</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed">To check your gas bill online, you need your consumer number. SNGPL uses an 11-digit number; SSGC uses a 10-digit number. Both are printed on the top section of your gas bill. This guide shows exactly where to find them.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Where is the SNGPL consumer number on the bill?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">The SNGPL consumer number is an 11-digit number printed in the top-left or top-center section of your SNGPL gas bill, labeled Consumer No. or Consumer Number. SNGPL covers Punjab, KPK, Islamabad, and AJK.</div></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Where is the SSGC consumer number?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">The SSGC consumer number is a 10-digit number on the top section of your SSGC gas bill. SSGC covers Sindh and Balochistan. The number is labeled Consumer No. near your name and address details.</div></details>
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">How to check SNGPL gas bill online?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">Go to pakistanbill.online/sngpl-bill/ and enter your 11-digit SNGPL consumer number. Your gas bill loads instantly showing amount due, due date, and units consumed. Free, no login required.</div></details>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-neutral-200 pt-6">
